mysql connector jar download(search in browser) --> maven repository --> search MySQL in serach tab --> MySQL Connector/J --> 9.1.0 --> jar(2.5 MB)

eclipse --> new java project --> jdbcprograms->right click on project -->  build path --> configure build path --> libraries --> click on class path--> add external jars --> add MySQL 9.1.0 in softwares folder --> apply --> apply and close

src --> new class --> com.codegnan.jdbcprograms --> CreateTable



